translated: Back, Karl Arvid, chief surveyor, Halmstad, b. 15/10/1900 in Västervik to vice-consul Carl B. and Emmy Jansson. Married on 25/xx to Cecilia Larsson. Children: Gunnar b. 1926, Ingrid b. 1927, Torsten b. 1929. - Graduated from high school in Västervik in 1919, graduated from surveyor school in 1922. Employed as surveyor in Stockholm 1923-1924, assistant to the head surveyor 1924-1927, surveyor in Östergötland county 1927-1929, acting district surveyor in Örnsköldsvik district 1929-1932, assistant in Gävle county 1932-1933, acting district surveyor in Undersåker district 1933-1934, district surveyor in Säter 1934-1939, temporary bureau director for the surveyor's board 1938-1939, chief surveyor in Halland county since 1939. Member of the local government board in Halmstad, awarded the Royal Order of the North Star.
